Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都是這個東西的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,發信器？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,被貼在他的腰帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也的位置才會因而暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是最初的那場戰鬥時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,確實那個大小的話是可以帶進「通靈塔」的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1315.734,973.6)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就算沒有幸也那樣特別的能力也行對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,對於 Hand Shakers 來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在現實中位置的暴露是相當危險的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不過   這樣就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你有趕上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,遲到了一會   給遙添了一些麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,DJ尼爾森
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我來給你們倒茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,從小代理那裡得知了   你很不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,和小代理小姐那時比起來   這不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,關於小代理以前的情況   你已經聽說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,現在也…還是一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我無論如何都會想辦法解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也和我十分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了很失禮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:05:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,假如你願意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能再一次和我一起進入「通靈塔」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1225.067,974.933)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡的「通靈塔」是有長岡先生他們的線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(722.667,974.933)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的   這是我和小代理第一次開始戰鬥的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只是和之前相比有點變化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,「寧錄」可以讓我看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(751.333,979.733)}Nimrod
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我給它取名為「Disc」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才擅自說你和我很相似   很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我和幸也是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我當時只是普通的學生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,現在依然是個非常平凡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一開始小代理可是無法使出「寧錄」的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(1280.666,977.066)}Nimrod
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你還沒找到搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,或許我們可以藉由你的能力來使用「寧錄」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(1401.333,978.399)}Nimrod
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才說我們很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而你那特殊的境遇和小代理也很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白那樣的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我想成為你的力量幫助你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不特別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此你還是會遭遇襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…大家都想要這樣的能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,擁有這樣的能力明明一點都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我也曾經很也厭惡與 Hand Shakers 之間的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,手綱先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候一直都很想逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡初次進入「通靈塔」時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1139.734,975.6)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,突然就被襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只能拼命的逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺很可怕啊   Hand Shakers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟他們賭上自己的願望戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…我並沒有什麼願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會成為 Hand Shakers 我自己也搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那時的我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不過…您不是見過神了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候的事情我已經記不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只是   在和小代理的戰鬥過程中我逐漸明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,自己到底想要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因此多少也變得比較強了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,只要明白了什麼就能變強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,人各有異吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,當初我只想保護可能會消失的小代理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,想讓她露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也許是有這種想法才使力量能夠注入「Single  Gear」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,也或許並非這樣的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,若覺得迷惘   捫心自問也是個不錯的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的那個 Disc   便是你心的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我仍然沒有想要保護的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HE8EB67&\fs55\pos(1098,373)}玩得很開心呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HE8EB67&\fs55\pos(1142,435)}能一起去真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HE8EB67&\fs55\pos(1078,589)}有機會再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,明明在她面前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,遙卻什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你想嘛   有什麼能夠贏過那位叫手綱的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙   究竟是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,發信器也被銷毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,本來那東西   就是要貼在那樣棘手的對手身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,為了能順利逃跑用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,卻反過來被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,話說他真的好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,使用 Disc 的人雖也很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可我面對手綱時   根本想不到能戰勝他的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要不乾脆放手一搏和他拚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,說行不通的是你好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,輸了就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是你還是我都只想在那個世界生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想前往宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,只要和你在一起就很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的也有道理   抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙我就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,為實現這個目的   必需要奪得 Disc 的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好   還要再和那兩個女人聯手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,「沒用的傢伙   笨蛋」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HA36B51&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(606,579)\frz10.18}沒用的傢伙。笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:10:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她們是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但你還有一招陰險的辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,早就安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有破綻的話那就由我們自己製造
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,唉   從副店長那裡收到好多訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不去了嗎   打工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,襲擊她之後怎麼還敢去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,高槻手綱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,實在是強的離譜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,妳已經和「Composer」商量過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,對手是高槻手綱很難有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs60\frz7.227\pos(592,499)}那是、高槻手綱。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs60\pos(746,755)\frz7.296}是謁見過神的 Hand Shakers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs60\frz7.384\pos(704,835)}對目前的妳們而言沒勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs60\frz7.227\pos(582,435)}那是、高槻手綱。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs60\frz7.655\pos(744,699)}是謁見過神的 Hand Shakers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs60\frz7.445\pos(704,783)}對目前的妳們而言沒勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,才一個「Y' s」就那麼棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不是完全沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,「Composer」說的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,何況他說我們只需牽手就能夠「充電」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(1343.467,975.8)}Charge
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們兩人的心只要緊緊相繫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,便能再增強「寧錄」的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(1019.333,979.733)}Nimrod
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這會是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這全部都是「Composer」告訴我們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果一直保持勝利 Hand Shakers 能力就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs40\pos(814,597)\frz6.25}請持續獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs40\frz7.26\pos(860,770.333)}只要保持戰績
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs40\pos(1050,803)\frz7.042}總有一天 Hand Shakers 能力就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs40\frz7.042\pos(1003.333,869.667)}妳們將無法再進入「通靈塔」了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs24\frz7.042\pos(1106.667,819)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,將無法再進到「通靈塔」了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1109.734,977.6)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,打敗「Y' s」   能力馬上就能消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法信任他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs60\frz7.227\pos(542,579)}那是、高槻手綱。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs60\pos(702,855)\frz7.645}是謁見過神的 Hand Shakers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HC7FD2A&\4c&HC7FD2A&\fs60\frz7.006\pos(664,939)}對目前的妳們而言沒勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只會用SNS來接近我們說明 Hand Shakers 的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至連臉都不曾見過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,至於其他能消除這個能力的方法我們也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要的又不是想變得更強之類的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想要自由的牽手而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.84,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fs70}哥哥當鬼   快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,小華
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不准弄哭千里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,什…什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是她自己要哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,小華
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小華~~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小華？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很難為情…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只有現在的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小華   今天打算去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那個   那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,千里…妳要搬家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天還是會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對…絕對會回到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前我們就一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,來牽手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小華
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想副店長大概已經聯絡給我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,下次可能就是找到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,假設我們瞄準好高槻手綱不在的時候攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,還是有機會的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,即使不用信任「Composer」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這個情報還是有價值的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3B3CDD&\3c&HB9B9F8&\4c&H1A1A9F&\fs100\org(1402.667,343.667)\frz347.5\pos(1437.334,365.001)}急   徵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC487F8&\3c&HEBD2F5&\4c&HE6BBF7&\fs90\pos(810.667,826.334)}谷 津 治        音 樂 祭 追 加 演 出 者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H50814F&\3c&HD5FF8E&\4c&HD5FF8E&\pos(816,1034.334)}音 樂 祭 的 參 加 者 募 集 中！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,「Y' s」想做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說尋找長岡先生他們是為了小代理小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可是這真的是我想做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,輕音部不是在練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一直練不好於是就逃出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說幸也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊   抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明還要煩惱「Y' s」的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是「通靈塔」？  被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(795.734,974.267)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄準了我落單的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…只是在我旁邊就被捲進來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這有可能嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把手給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是「Connect」她們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會找到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要逃了喔   現在先跟著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒…沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這次絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不會再讓你逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,和「Composer」說的一樣   真的變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:17:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也總是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,從以前   從小的時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是叫做小遙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是剛搬進隔壁的荒城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙是幸也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他有點怕生   希望請妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會打招呼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不行喔   幸也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就讓我來當你的姊姊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我是土佐堀遙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,HA…RU…KA…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,去和小遙一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,從「通靈塔」出來後   幾乎不怎麼說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(638.401,975.6)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這會是個好的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,原本我應該是姊姊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只不過…幸也漸漸的改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,總會站在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一直被幸也所拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而我…卻對他說了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也   你快走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我會積極振作的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,別露出那種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,當結束時妳全部都會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真頑強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小華
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是要把自己的心意全部傳達給對方才會更強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯   那我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,妳對我太關心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我會保護妳的   千里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,小華   最愛妳了
